command.text: M82 ; Set absolute mode for extruder
M999 ; Reset from a halted state
M84 ; Disable steppers so that the Z axis returns to center
G4P100 ; Wait half a second for the Z axis to settle
G92 Z0 ; Tell Smoothie that Z is now at 0
G92 Y0 X0 A0 B0 ; Tell Smoothie that Y is now at 0
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:B%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
G4 P250 ; pause for a given duration of time - 1 second, todo 250ms
G4 P250 ; pause for a given duration of time - 1 second, todo 250ms
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:A%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:B%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
M105 ; read all temperatures and vacuum levels
M600 N{IntegerValue} F4 X1 ; feeder N0 advance tape 4mm ignoring errors
M600 N{IntegerValue} F8 ; feeder N0 advance tape 4mm ignoring errors
M600 N{IntegerValue} F12 ; feeder N0 advance tape 4mm ignoring errors
M601 N{IntegerValue} ; retract advancing lever (next time feed is faster, this command is a post-pick command)
